llm_results: [{"detection_name": "LLM: sql_injection", "detection": "vulnerable", "category": "Injection Attacks", "description": "The 'title' field within the 'updatePhoto' mutation's response reflects an SQL injection payload: \"'; SELECT SLEEP(5); --\".
